celebrates with her;

279
00:17:07,339 --> 00:17:08,800
and whoever arrives later

280
00:17:09,190 --> 00:17:11,400
stays out of her life and never shows up
in front of her again.

281
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:12,530
How does that sound?

282
00:17:15,599 --> 00:17:17,710
She's a very interesting girl.

283
00:17:17,950 --> 00:17:19,430
You like her?

284
00:17:23,750 --> 00:17:24,550
Get in the car.

285
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:33,880
Put on your earphones and don't hang up.

286
00:17:37,030 --> 00:17:39,090
Any other rules?
Say them all at once.

287
00:17:40,320 --> 00:17:41,360
No, that's all.

288
00:18:27,250 --> 00:18:28,510
Want me to wait for you?

289
00:18:28,990 --> 00:18:29,640
No need.

290
00:18:30,360 --> 00:18:31,090
You go first.

291
00:18:31,230 --> 00:18:32,880
The red light lasts for tens of seconds.

292
00:18:32,880 --> 00:18:35,680
