it feels like an unfair win.

293
00:18:35,910 --> 00:18:36,910
Only if you beat me

294
00:18:36,990 --> 00:18:40,320
will you have a chance to talk about
whether it's fair or not.

295
00:18:41,120 --> 00:18:42,190
Anyway,

296
00:18:42,710 --> 00:18:44,030
your driving skills are quite good.

297
00:18:44,030 --> 00:18:44,840
Just average.

298
00:18:45,600 --> 00:18:46,750
I'm just driving for fun.

299
00:18:46,750 --> 00:18:48,670
You're better with words.

300
00:18:48,990 --> 00:18:50,720
Don't you understand sarcasm?

301
00:18:52,680 --> 00:18:53,600
So if I win,

302
00:18:54,110 --> 00:18:56,270
you'll accept defeat nicely, right?

303
00:19:00,270 --> 00:19:01,330
Three minutes ago,

304
00:19:01,930 --> 00:19:03,990
you had the chance to state the rules.

305
00:19:14,190 --> 00:19:16,320
Your start was faster than I expected.

306
00:19:16,320 --> 00:19:18,600
You have even more OEM parts
than I thought.

307
00:19:18,600 --> 00:19:19,730
It could be lighter.

308
00:19:28,900 --> 00:19:30,950
Then how would you
deal with the counterweight?

309
00:19:30,950 --> 00:19:32,030
I don't work for you.

310
00:19:32,030 --> 00:19:33,600
I can pay you.

311
00:19:34,130 --> 00:19:35,060
But I don't sell.

312
00:19:47,800 --> 00:19:49,640
My HP is 500. What about you?

313
00:19:49,710 --> 00:19:50,270
600.

314
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:51,270
A Wankel engine

315
00:19:51,270 --> 00:19:53,160
can reach up to 650 HP.

316
00:19:53,750 --> 00:19:56,230
If you had increased
your turbo boost a bit,

317
00:19:56,470 --> 00:19:58,460
overtaking just now would've been easier.

318
00:19:58,460 --> 00:19:59,430
The factory setting is 0.5,

319
00:19:59,430 --> 00:20:00,430
and now it's 0.8.

320
00:20:00,670 --> 00:20:02,270
It could be increased to 1.0.

321
00:20:02,370 --> 00:20:03,500
It's enough as it is.

322
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:09,690
Are those your people?

323
00:20:09,690 --> 00:20:11,170
Have you played Klotski?

324
00:20:13,160 --> 00:20:14,490
A game for 3-year-olds.

325
00:20:38,710 --> 00:20:40,470
Your Wankel engine has more HP

326
00:20:41,140 --> 00:20:42,370
and your car is lighter.

327
00:20:42,370 --> 00:20:43,920
If we're talking pure performance,
I'm bound to lose.

328
00:20:43,920 --> 00:20:46,920
I'm just racing with a twin-rotor engine
at top speed.

329
00:20:47,600 --> 00:20:49,120
Why are you so fixated on rotors?

330
00:20:49,120 --> 00:20:50,920
Guess why I won't buy your parts?

331
00:20:50,920 --> 00:20:53,190
