334
00:20:56,030 --> 00:20:57,890
That's exactly what I had in mind.

335
00:20:59,360 --> 00:21:00,840
Then I'll wait and see.

336
00:21:35,430 --> 00:21:36,640
Your brakes are very responsive.

337
00:21:36,640 --> 00:21:37,610
Did you modify them yourself?

338
00:21:37,610 --> 00:21:38,210
Yes.

339
00:21:38,400 --> 00:21:39,860
I upgraded my brake discs,

340
00:21:40,080 --> 00:21:41,230
and I modified the calipers too.

341
00:21:41,230 --> 00:21:42,760
So where am I falling short?

342
00:21:42,920 --> 00:21:44,880
Your suspension is too soft.
It can't hold up,

343
00:21:44,880 --> 00:21:45,640
and that causes a chain reaction.

344
00:21:45,640 --> 00:21:46,500
Anything else?

345
00:21:46,640 --> 00:21:48,470
