and the coilovers

346
00:21:48,470 --> 00:21:50,600
and piston calipers are all replicas.

347
00:21:50,640 --> 00:21:51,800
This isn't the optimal setup.

348
00:21:51,800 --> 00:21:54,200
You've never driven it—how would you know?

349
00:21:54,560 --> 00:21:55,290
I can hear it.

350
00:21:55,360 --> 00:21:56,620
I underestimated you.

351
00:22:12,800 --> 00:22:13,670
That night before taking the corner,

352
00:22:13,670 --> 00:22:15,870
