353
00:22:17,620 --> 00:22:20,030
Racing cars, underground fighting.

354
00:22:20,500 --> 00:22:22,700
Do you own that Chinese restaurant too?

355
00:22:24,600 --> 00:22:26,860
Who's that drunk man who's always there?

356
00:22:27,090 --> 00:22:28,510
How long have you been into racing?

357
00:22:28,510 --> 00:22:30,470
Why haven't I seen you in Manshi before?

358
00:22:30,470 --> 00:22:32,000
You have so many questions.

359
00:22:32,070 --> 00:22:34,600
Then why aren't you answering them?

360
00:22:34,840 --> 00:22:35,950
Why are you

361
00:22:36,040 --> 00:22:37,700
so interested in my business?

362
00:22:44,800 --> 00:22:46,990
Taking corners fast
is what makes you truly fast.

363
00:22:46,990 --> 00:22:48,950
Step on the gas pedal
immediately after the turn

364
00:22:48,950 --> 00:22:50,360
to exit the turn faster.

365
00:22:53,670 --> 00:22:54,530
How about this?

366
00:22:54,710 --> 00:22:56,470
From now on, I'll lead—

367
00:22:56,800 --> 00:22:57,730
will you follow?

368
00:22:58,030 --> 00:22:58,920
Sure.

369
00:23:09,510 --> 00:23:10,800
You did that on purpose.

370
00:23:10,800 --> 00:23:12,460
I didn't plant those flowers.

371
00:23:14,710 --> 00:23:15,880
Turn off your navigation

372
00:23:15,880 --> 00:23:16,600
and stay close behind me.

373
00:23:16,600 --> 00:23:18,040
You're not setting me up, are you?

374
00:23:18,040 --> 00:23:19,040
What do you think?

375
00:23:24,120 --> 00:23:25,850
Ma'am, I'm heading back first.

376
00:23:28,870 --> 00:23:31,000
Zhao! Driving really fast today, huh?

377
00:23:37,920 --> 00:23:39,800
I believe you did this on purpose
this time.

378
00:23:39,800 --> 00:23:40,990
I told you to stay close.

379
00:23:40,990 --> 00:23:42,590
It was you who didn't keep up.

380
00:24:01,140 --> 00:24:02,540
You need to be so skilled

381
00:24:02,950 --> 00:24:04,750
