390
00:24:58,750 --> 00:24:59,880
I was being foolish.

391
00:25:00,710 --> 00:25:02,990
I lost my sense of proportion
in the heat of the moment.

392
00:25:02,990 --> 00:25:05,670
I shouldn't have treated public roads
as racetracks.

393
00:25:05,670 --> 00:25:06,930
You taught me a lesson.

394
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:10,680
I'm leaving. Won't wait for you.

